Pros: 15 minutes away from Buckroe Beach and the major hwy
Cons: Process of check-in after confirmation of booking and early check-in reservations; female front desk representative did not have a pleasant nor welcoming attitude upon arrival, she didn’t greet guest upon arriving just starred; hallways were not vacuumed and stairs were extremely dated and dusty; Continental breakfast is offered but because of the pandemic breakfast is cereal, fruit, granola bar no milk in a bag and reservations are still
Being charged for continental breakfast rates; third party reservation guest are treated as second class customers; linen and towels dinghy ;
